name: VES MAGUS #002
description:
When an alien virus infected the world humans and machines bonded. We escaped into the virtual world to fight for our existence. This is new URTH an original series featuring an array of original characters.
VES MAGUS is a living nightmare. He runs the battlefield collecting the dead to reassemble into reanimated abominations.

This is a special character edition not available for purchase and is a gift from me to those early adopters of my URTH series. An official release version of Ves will be available in the near future.
